GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 8 September, 2003
17 Bhadrapada, 1925(S)
The undersigned is directed to say that the following Ministers were sworn
in by the President at 1300 hours, today, the 8th September, 2003, in the
Rashtrapati Bhawan, New Delhi:-
Cabinet Ministers
Kum. Mamata Banerjee
Ministers of State
Shri Gingee N. Ramachandran
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:-
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
Director (Cabinet).
...2/-

- 2 -

Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)

Secretaries to the Govt. of India/Chairman, Railway Board/Accounts Officer, Pay
& Accounts Office, Cabinet Affairs, for information.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
Director (Cabinet).
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the Govt. of India/Lok
Sabha Secretariat (Question Branch)/Rajya Sabha Secretariat (Question
Branch)/ Establishment Officer, Department of Personnel & Training/Ministry of
External Affairs (Protocol Division)/Press Information Bureau/Section Officer,
NGO Section, Prime Minister's Office.
